(37, 3, '2012-08-21 23:01:15', '2012-08-21 23:01:15', '<h1>Transition House</h1>\r\nThe Transition House provides short term shelter and related services to women, youth and children who have experienced or are at risk of violence. As a safe shelter with support, women are enabled to make decisions about their future and gain increased awareness of the nature of abuse.\r\n<h1><strong>Homeless Prevention Program </strong></h1>\r\nThe Homeless Prevention Program  assists women who have experienced violence and are homeless or at risk of homelessness to find and /or maintain housing.  This includes women leaving corrections and hospital systems.\r\n\r\nSupport include:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Directly engaging to asses individual and family\'s needs with housing</li>\r\n	<li>Connecting to affordable housing</li>\r\n	<li>Referring to appropriate resources</li>\r\n	<li>Providing rental supplements if eligible</li>\r\n	<li>Providing ongoing support and follow</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nFor a confidential intake please call 250-558-0171', 'Transition House', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'transition-house', '', '', '2016-08-30 17:19:25', '2016-08-30 17:19:25', '', 29, 'http://localhost/transition-house/?page_id=37', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(444, 3, '2012-10-01 21:45:49', '2012-10-01 21:45:49', '<h1>Women’s Counselling: Armstrong &amp; Enderby</h1>\r\nWe offer free, accessible and confidential counselling services to women who have experienced violence or abuse. We work to assist women in their healing with support, awareness and education.\r\n\r\nThe counselling services available focus on the needs of the woman. We regard her safety and that of her children as paramount.\r\n<h2>Services we offer:</h2>\r\n• Confidential individual and/or group counselling services to women based on the needs of women.\r\n• A safe environment to look at personal safety, feelings and the effects of abuse.\r\n• Support, information and encouragement to help women discover their strengths.\r\n• Referral services to other support agencies that will help women in their recovery process.', 'Women’s Counselling: Armstrong/ Enderby', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '41-revision-v1', '', '', '2012-10-01 21:45:49', '2012-10-01 21:45:49', '', 41, 'http://localhost/wordpress/2012/10/41-revision-12/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
