(789, 2, '2013-11-25 19:04:59', '2013-11-25 19:04:59', '<strong>THANK YOU TO OKANAGAN RESTORATION</strong>\r\n\r\nWe would like to thank <em>Okanagan Restoration</em> - <em>Shane and Andy</em>, for their generous donation of time to paint the interior of our Residence.  As a shelter for 25 women and children seeking shelter from domestic abuse it is important that our Transition House is a warm and welcoming place.  We were also impressed by the professionalism and pride that Shane and Andy took in their work.  Having the kitchen painted has made a world of difference to the main floor.\r\n\r\nThis donation has greatly improved the look and feel of our Transition House and we greatly appreciate it.\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #8d3e54;\"><em><strong>Thank you from the Staff and Residents</strong></em></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #8d3e54;\"><em><strong>of </strong></em></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #8d3e54;\"><em><strong>Vernon Women\'s Transition House.</strong></em></span></p>', 'Interior Repainted at Transition House', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'interior-repainted-at-transition-house', '', '', '2014-06-09 18:47:42', '2014-06-09 18:47:42', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=789', 0, 'post', '', 0),
