(384, 3, '2012-09-07 22:43:20', '2012-09-07 22:43:20', '<h1>Support to Young Parents</h1>\r\nThe Support to Young Parents Program provides affordable housing and support to pregnant and parenting teens and young women (ages 15-24).\r\n<h2>The services include:</h2>\r\n• One or two bedroom apartment with affordable rent.\r\n• Free utilities, laundry and cable.\r\n• Security system and monitoring.\r\n• Furniture and household items are available on a limited basis.', 'Support to Young Parents', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '49-revision-v1', '', '', '2012-09-07 22:43:20', '2012-09-07 22:43:20', '', 49, 'http://localhost/wordpress/2012/09/49-revision-6/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
