(390, 3, '2012-10-01 18:25:50', '2012-10-01 18:25:50', '<h1>\r\nWish List</h1>\r\nWe have complied this Wish List as a guideline to let you know our greatest needs. Thank you for your generousity! Please contact us at 250-542-1185 for more information.\r\n<h2>General Items</h2>\r\n•  Long distance phone cards\r\n•  City transit passes\r\n•  Video rental certificates\r\n•  Movie coupons, passes to rec centre, pool, fitness centres\r\n•  Alarm clocks\r\n•  Night lights\r\n•  Journals and pens\r\n•  Pocket size personal calendars\r\n•  Key chains\r\n•  Nintendo, N64 games\r\n•  Food and groceries of all kinds, but especially “fun” food like frozen pizzas <em>(Please note we cannot accept home canning).</em>\r\n•  Craft kits and supplies (simple embroidery kits, needles and yarn)\r\n•  Suitcases\r\n•  Cash donations are always needed and welcomed\r\n<h2>Household Items (Gently-used items in working condition)</h2>\r\n•  Microwaves\r\n•  TVs\r\n•  Mattresses\r\n•  Dishes, cutlery, utensils, pots &amp; pans\r\n•  Dining tables and chairs, couches, coffee and end tables\r\n* Please note that we cannot accept cabinet TVs, hide-a-beds or desks.\r\n<h2>Toiletries and Personal Hygiene</h2>\r\n•  Brushes and combs\r\n•  Covered elastics for hair, barrettes, etc.\r\n•  Tweezers, new nail clippers and other manicure items\r\n•  Toiletries, sanitary supplies, deodorant', 'Wish List', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '343-revision-v1', '', '', '2012-10-01 18:25:50', '2012-10-01 18:25:50', '', 343, 'http://localhost/wordpress/2012/10/343-revision-6/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1373, 3, '2015-05-01 17:10:32', '2015-05-01 17:10:32', '<h1>Contact Us</h1>\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">For donations of household items, please call the Transition House directly\r\nat 250-542-1122.</span></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Vernon Women\'s Transition House Society\r\nMailing Address: </strong>PO Box 625, Vernon, BC  V1T 6M6\r\n<strong>Administration Office: </strong>The People Place - 3402 27th Ave. Room #302.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n[Contact_Form_Builder id=\"2\"]', 'Contact', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1336-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-01 17:10:32', '2015-05-01 17:10:32', '', 1336, 'http://localhost/wordpress/2015/05/1336-revision-36/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(394, 3, '2012-09-11 02:05:17', '2012-09-11 02:05:17', '<h1>Women’s Counselling: Armstrong &amp; Enderby</h1>\r\nWe offer free, accessible and confidential counselling services to women who have experienced violence or abuse. We work to assist women in their healing with support, awareness and education.\r\n\r\nThe counselling services available focus on the needs of the woman. We regard her safety and that of her children as paramount.\r\n<h2>Services we offer:</h2>\r\n• Confidential individual and/or group counselling services to women based on the needs of women.\r\n• A safe environment to look at personal safety, feelings and the effects of abuse.\r\n• Support, information and encouragement to help women discover their strengths.\r\n• Referral services to other support agencies that will help women in their recovery process.', 'Women’s Counselling: Armstrong/ Enderby', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '41-revision-v1', '', '', '2012-09-11 02:05:17', '2012-09-11 02:05:17', '', 41, 'http://localhost/wordpress/2012/09/41-revision-11/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(395, 3, '2012-09-11 02:23:57', '2012-09-11 02:23:57', '<h1>Women’s Counselling: Vernon</h1>\r\nWe offer free, accessible and confidential counseling services to women who have experienced violence or abuse. We work to assist women in their healing with support, awareness and education.\r\n\r\nThe counselling services available focus on the needs of the woman. We regard her safety and that of her children as paramount.\r\n<h2>Services we offer:</h2>\r\n• Confidential individual and/or group counselling services to women based on the needs of women.\r\n• A safe environment to look at personal safety, feelings and the effects of abuse.\r\n• Support, information and encouragement to help women discover their strengths.\r\n• Referral services to other support agencies that will help women in their recovery process.', 'Women’s Counselling: Vernon', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '43-revision-v1', '', '', '2012-09-11 02:23:57', '2012-09-11 02:23:57', '', 43, 'http://localhost/wordpress/2012/09/43-revision-7/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(396, 3, '2012-09-07 22:08:31', '2012-09-07 22:08:31', '<h1>Law Clinic</h1>\r\nDo you need some legal advice, or think you might? We can help you with criminal law, family law or any other legal issue. If you don’t know where to turn and cannot afford a lawyer, let us help you.\r\n\r\nAttend the FREE Legal Clinic\r\n\r\nClinics are held on Thursdays of each month, except statutory holidays.', 'Law Clinic', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '71-revision-v1', '', '', '2012-09-07 22:08:31', '2012-09-07 22:08:31', '', 71, 'http://localhost/wordpress/2012/09/71-revision-4/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1427, 2, '2015-09-08 22:00:26', '2015-09-08 22:00:26', '<h1>Law Clinic - Please contact the toll free Access Pro Bono phone number to book an appointment.  <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">1-877-762-6664.</span></h1>\r\n<strong>Provided by <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Volunteer Lawyers</span></strong>.\r\n<h2><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">IMPORTANT NOTICE:</span></strong></h2>\r\n<h2><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">The Free Legal Clinic has moved to a new location.</span> </strong> <strong>The new address is #102 - 3301 24th Ave., Vernon BC.</strong></h2>\r\nDo you need some legal advice, or think you might? We can help you receive basic advice on legal issues from a lawyer.\r\n\r\n<em>Appointments are booked on a first come, first served basis.</em>\r\n\r\nSome issues may not be addressed at every clinic - you may have to wait for another session when a volunteer lawyer is available who can assist you.\r\n<h2>Attend the FREE Legal Clinic</h2>\r\nClinics are held on Thursdays of each month<em> (when a volunteer lawyer is available),</em> except statutory holidays.', 'Law Clinic', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '71-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-09-08 22:00:26', '2015-09-08 22:00:26', '', 71, 'http://localhost/wordpress/2015/09/71-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(557, 3, '2012-10-01 21:50:00', '2012-10-01 21:50:00', '<h1>Law Clinic</h1>\r\nDo you need some legal advice, or think you might? We can help you with criminal law, family law or any other legal issue. If you don’t know where to turn and cannot afford a lawyer, let us help you.\r\n\r\nAttend the FREE Legal Clinic\r\n\r\nClinics are held on Thursdays of each month, except statutory holidays.', 'Law Clinic', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '71-revision-v1', '', '', '2012-10-01 21:50:00', '2012-10-01 21:50:00', '', 71, 'http://localhost/wordpress/2012/10/71-revision-5/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
