(447, 3, '2012-09-11 02:28:40', '2012-09-11 02:28:40', '<h1>Women’s Outreach Services</h1>\r\nWomen and their dependant children who have experience violence, abuse and threats from an intimate partner can access help from the Outreach Program.\r\n<h2>The Program provides:</h2>\r\n• Mobile response and supportive counselling.\r\n• Support at a safe location in your community.\r\n• Service at the Outreach office.\r\n• Outreach service at other community agencies.', 'Women’s Outreach Services', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '46-revision-v1', '', '', '2012-09-11 02:28:40', '2012-09-11 02:28:40', '', 46, 'http://localhost/wordpress/2012/09/46-revision-7/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
