(769, 2, '2013-10-15 22:18:36', '2013-10-15 22:18:36', '<a href=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/RenoSign.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-770 alignleft\" title=\"RenoSign\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/RenoSign-300x296.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"168\" height=\"160\" /></a>\r\n\r\nThe Vernon Women\'s Transition House Society is presently raising funds towards renovating our 11 bedrooms for clients.  Our Transition House is 20 years old and is needing some TLC.  Funds received from our ongoing fundraising campaign will be used for paint, flooring and baseboards, new bed frames and storage drawers, mattresses, bedding and decor for the walls.  As a shelter for some of our most vulnerable community members, we would like to create a warm and welcoming space for the women and children who reside with us.\r\n\r\nWe are looking to our generous community to assist us with accomplishing our renovation project.  In the event a community member or business is willing to donate funds to completely renovate one of our bedrooms, a charitable tax receipt for the amount donated will be provided and the donor will be recognized with a plaque located in the bedroom they have generously assisted to renovate.  All donations of funds, materials or manpower are greatly appreciated.\r\n\r\nIn the event that you would like to assist us with this project, please contact <strong>Brooke McLardy, Programs Director</strong> at <strong>250.542.1122</strong> or at <a href=\"mailto:brooke.mclardy@vwts.ca\">brooke.mclardy@vwts.ca</a>.\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Our sincere<em><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong> thank you</strong> </span></em>to the following community organizations who have so graciously donated to our renovation fund</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Nixon Wenger</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Rotary Club of Vernon</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>New Car Dealers Association of Vernon</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Home Depot</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Rona</strong></p>', 'UNDER RENOVATION', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'under-renovation', '', '', '2014-06-09 18:47:58', '2014-06-09 18:47:58', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=769', 0, 'post', '', 0),
