zers, nail clippers and other manicure items (New Only)</li>\r\n	<li>Toiletries, sanitary supplies, new deodorant</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Wish List', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '343-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-12-09 19:05:36', '2013-12-09 19:05:36', '', 343, 'http://localhost/wordpress/2013/12/343-revision-17/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
