(818, 2, '2013-12-17 00:19:36', '2013-12-17 00:19:36', '<a href=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/EquineTherapydonation-20132.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-822 aligncenter\" title=\"EquineTherapydonation 2013\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/EquineTherapydonation-20132-300x246.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"417\" height=\"343\" /></a>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Wendy Elrick (left, of Vernon Women\'s Transition House, and Susy Bairstow, of the B.C. Interior Horse Rescue Society, receive $3,700 cash each from Sheila Sperling and Ruby Edwards, with the Horsey Ladies.</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><em>Morning Star Staff</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">They came from all over the Interior to socialize, shop and to give back to charity.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">And once again, the annual Okanagan Horsey Ladies Charity Auction proved it has what it takes to give back to the community.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The 16th annual event, at the Spallumcheen Golf and Country Club, brought together 130 women who nominated a total of 12 charities to support that evening.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The top two vote-getters were the B.C. Interior Horse Rescue Society and <strong>Vernon Women\'s Transition House\'s Equine Assisted Therapy Program</strong>.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><em>\"We are pleased to announce, thanks to the generosity of our sponsors and the ladies bidding, we raised $7,400 (exceeding last year\'s $6,400),\"</em> said Nancy Roman, spokesperson for the Horsey Ladies committee.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><em>\"The amount was divided equally and $3,700 was given to each winning charity.\"</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The group has raised a total of $57,000 since beginning its annual fundraisers.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><em>\"The Horsey Ladies is neither a club nor a society, we have no president of bank account,\"</em> said Roman.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><em>\"We are just a bunch of gals that get together and meet at Christmas and seek out donations throughout the year.  We appreciate and tank all of the local and out-of-town sponsors.\"</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Besides Roman, the other members of the Horsey Ladies are Ruby Edwards, Elspeth Manning, Michele Gould, Amy Vaughan, Sheila Sperling, Patti Thomas and Ursula McHugh.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"> </p>\r\n&nbsp;', 'EQUINE THERAPY RECEIVES DONATION', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'equine-therapy-receives-donation', '', '', '2014-06-09 18:47:09', '2014-06-09 18:47:09', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=818', 0, 'post', '', 0),
