(840, 3, '2012-12-06 23:24:39', '2012-12-06 23:24:39', '<h1>Law Clinic</h1>\r\nDo you need some legal advice, or think you might? We can help you receive basic advice on legal issues from a lawyer.\r\n<h2>Attend the FREE Legal Clinic</h2>\r\nClinics are held on Thursdays of each month, except statutory holidays.', 'Law Clinic', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '71-revision-v1', '', '', '2012-12-06 23:24:39', '2012-12-06 23:24:39', '', 71, 'http://localhost/wordpress/2012/12/71-revision-6/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
