(844, 3, '2012-11-01 19:11:37', '2012-11-01 19:11:37', '<h1>Transition House</h1>\r\nThe Transition House provides short term shelter and related services to women, youth and children who have experienced or are at risk of violence. As a safe shelter with support, women are enabled to make decisions about their future and gain increased awareness of the nature of abuse.', 'Transition House', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '37-revision-v1', '', '', '2012-11-01 19:11:37', '2012-11-01 19:11:37', '', 37, 'http://localhost/wordpress/2012/11/37-revision-5/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
