(846, 2, '2013-07-08 17:35:00', '2013-07-08 17:35:00', '<h1>Legal Advocacy Program</h1>\r\nAn advocate may help you understand information on:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>your rights and options</li>\r\n	<li>reconsideration requests</li>\r\n	<li>tribunals</li>\r\n	<li>procedures and investigations</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAn advocate may also:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>provide information and referrals</li>\r\n	<li>help with writing letters, applications and forms</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>A legal advocate cannot give legal advice.</strong>', 'Legal Advocacy Program', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '67-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-07-08 17:35:00', '2013-07-08 17:35:00', '', 67, 'http://localhost/wordpress/2013/07/67-revision-13/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
