(876, 2, '2014-01-13 18:59:01', '2014-01-13 18:59:01', '<h2><span style=\"color: #7d3a46;\"><strong>THANK YOU TO VERNON AND DISTRICT WOMEN\'S CENTRE</strong>:</span></h2>\r\nIt was a bittersweet moment.\r\n\r\nWe were gifted with a significant donation for the women and children we serve but it came at the cost of a local agency.\r\n\r\nThe Vernon and District Women\'s Centre closed its doors in May 2011.\r\n\r\nThe board has remained active and hopeful that the political climate would change and funding to continue their work with vulnerable women in our community could continue.\r\n\r\nThis, unfortunately, has not been the case.\r\n\r\nThe board of the Women\'s Centre is preparing to dissolve and in doing so has generously gifted their remaining funds to continue to assist women and children.\r\n\r\nWe extend a heartfelt thank you to the board for this meaningful gift with we plan to put towards running groups for women who have experienced violence, mental ill health and substance use issues and to continue our work to prevent violence against women and children in our community.\r\n\r\nAgain, <em>Thank you.</em>\r\n\r\nBrooke McLardy, Programs Director and Ninke Beeksma, Executive Director - Vernon Women\'s Transition House Society', 'THANK YOU', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'thank-you', '', '', '2014-06-09 18:46:44', '2014-06-09 18:46:44', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=876', 0, 'post', '', 0);
