(1324, 2, '2015-04-27 23:28:10', '2015-04-27 23:28:10', '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/RotaryClub1.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-1325 aligncenter\" title=\"RotaryClub1\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/RotaryClub1-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"218\" height=\"151\" /></a></p>\r\nWe would like to thank the Vernon Rotary Club for their efforts toward clean up at our Transition House on April 25th.  Their hard work was greatly appreciated.\r\n\r\nAlso, we thank the Vernon Rotary Club for their donation of $500 to our Transition House.  All support we receive greatly benefits the women and children we serve at Vernon Women\'s Transition House.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/RotaryClub2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1326\" title=\"RotaryClub2\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/RotaryClub2-194x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"142\" height=\"236\" /></a><a href=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/RotaryClub3.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1327\" title=\"RotaryClub3\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/RotaryClub3-204x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"147\" height=\"238\" /></a><a href=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/RotaryClub41.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1330\" title=\"RotaryClub4\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/RotaryClub41-198x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"142\" height=\"235\" /></a>', 'VERNON ROTARY CLUB WORK DAY - APRIL 25th, 2015', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'vernon-rotary-club-work-day-april-25th-2015', '', '', '2015-04-27 23:28:10', '2015-04-27 23:28:10', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=1324', 0, 'post', '', 0),
