(1083, 2, '2014-08-05 20:53:22', '2014-08-05 20:53:22', '<a href=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/BrookeArtDonation2014.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-1084\" title=\"BrookeArtDonation2014\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/BrookeArtDonation2014-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<em>Photo by Lisa McMullin</em>.\r\n\r\nBrooke McLardy (Left), VWTHS Programs Director with her artist-teacher Linda Hunt (Right) and their painting titled <strong><em>\"Transition\"</em> </strong>which was auctioned off for $850.<em> </em>\r\n\r\nA total of <strong>$8,457.60</strong> was raised through at the first annual charity event held by <em>The Rise Community Association</em> (RCA) held on July 5, 2014 on Johnny\'s Patio at The Rise.  Eleven pieces of art were auctioned off as was a furniture set donated by <em>Beachcomber Home Leisure</em>.  All of the money raised will be used to purchase new beds for the Transition House.\r\n\r\nNewspaper Articles:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.vernonmorningstar.com/entertainment/263553811.html\">http://www.vernonmorningstar.com/entertainment/263553811.html</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.vernonmorningstar.com/entertainment/266299251.html\">http://www.vernonmorningstar.com/entertainment/266299251.html</a>', 'THE RISE COMMUNITY ASSOCIATION - First Annual Charity Event', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'donation-the-rise-community-association-2', '', '', '2014-08-05 22:58:09', '2014-08-05 22:58:09', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=1083', 0, 'post', '', 0),
