(1105, 2, '2014-09-03 16:00:47', '2014-09-03 16:00:47', 'We would like to thank the <strong>Canadian Women\'s Foundation</strong>, in partnership with <strong>Winners / HomeSense and Rogers Media</strong>, for donating <strong>$1,733</strong> raised through the Canadian Women\'s Foundation\'s tenth <em>Annual Campaign to End Violence Against Women</em>.  This campaign took place from <em>April 12th to May 11th 2014</em>.  To learn more about this Annual Campaign, please visit their website: <a href=\"http://www.canadianwomen.org/annualviolencecampaign\">www.canadianwomen.org/annualviolencecampaign</a>.\r\n\r\nThe funds we received were raised through the following activities:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The sale of Shop for Hope special merchandise and decal sales at Winners and HomeSense,</li>\r\n	<li>Individual donations made on-line.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThis campaign raised a national total of $2 million.  Half of the money raised is divided amongst approximately 450 shelters for abused women across Canada <em>(with charitable status registered with the Canada Revenue Agency),</em> and half goes toward violence prevention programs funded by the Canadian Women\'s Foundation.', 'DONATION - Canadian Women\'s Foundation', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'donation-canadian-womens-foundation', '', '', '2014-09-03 16:00:47', '2014-09-03 16:00:47', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=1105', 0, 'post', '', 0),
