(1107, 2, '2014-09-03 16:00:22', '2014-09-03 16:00:22', 'We would like to thank the <strong>Canadian Women\'s Foundation</strong>, in partnership with <strong>Winners / HomeSense and Rogers Media</strong>, for donating <strong>$1,733</strong> raised through the Canadian Women\'s Foundation\'s tenth <em>Annual Campaign to End Violence Against Women</em>.  This campaign took place from <em>April 12th to May 11th 2014</em>.  To learn more about this Annual Campaign, please visit their website: <a href=\"http://www.canadianwomen.org/annualviolencecampaign\">www.canadianwomen.org/annualviolencecampaign</a>.\n\nThe funds we received were raised through the following activities:\n<ul>\n	<li>The sale of Shop for Hope special merchandise and decal sales at Winners and HomeSense,</li>\n	<li>Individual donations made on-line.</li>\n</ul>\nThis campaign raised a national total of $2 million.  Half of the money raised is divided amongst approximately 450 shelters for abused women across Canada <em>(with charitable status registered with the Canada Revenue Agency),</em> and half goes toward violence prevention programs funded by the Canadian Women\'s Foundation.', 'DONATION - Canadian Women\'s Foundation', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1105-revision-2', '', '', '2014-09-03 16:00:22', '2014-09-03 16:00:22', '', 1105, 'http://localhost/wordpress/2014/09/1105-revision-2/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
