(1146, 2, '2014-10-06 16:13:24', '2014-10-06 16:13:24', 'The Vernon Women\'s Transition House Society is pleased to announce that our <em><strong>North Okanagan Child Advocacy Centre Partnership</strong> </em>has received a <strong>$25,000</strong> grant from the <em><strong>Department of Justice Canada</strong></em>.  This money will be used to develop a framework for a Child Abuse Response service and future Child Advocacy Centre in Vernon.  Members of the North Okanagan Child Advocacy Centre Partnership include RCMP, Ministry of Children and Family Development, Sexual Assault Service (Vernon Jubilee Hospital), Family Resource Centre Society for the North Okanagan and North Okanagan Youth and Family Services Society in addition to many other community stakeholders.', 'Grant Money Received for Child Advocacy Centre', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1145-revision', '', '', '2014-10-06 16:13:24', '2014-10-06 16:13:24', '', 1145, 'http://localhost/wordpress/2014/10/1145-revision/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
