(1219, 2, '2015-01-28 21:29:17', '2015-01-28 21:29:17', 'The Vernon Women\'s Transition House Society is a charitable organization, relying significantly on government funds to implement and maintain our programs and services in our community.  We are extremely grateful for the ongoing support we receive from individuals and businesses within our community to complement our services to women and children in need.  These contributions make a real difference to the level of service we can provide!\r\n\r\nAlthough we cannot recognize every donation individually, we wish to express our sincere appreciation to all those who help us:\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n	<li>Community members and organizations who generously give of their resources, whether it be cash donations, furniture and household items, personal and hygiene items, or other general items.  These donations are always put to good use for the women and children in the house or when they leave it helps them (re) build their home.</li>\r\n	<li>Volunteer involvement adds value to the programming we provide.  Extra activities and attention offered to our clients have a huge impact on their journey through difficult times.</li>\r\n	<li>Businesses continue to provide generously, sometimes financially, sometimes through free labour and/or materials.  This support helps us to maintain our facilities, so that it can be a safe haven for all who utilize our services.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #9c2531;\"><strong>PLEASE KNOW THAT YOUR SUPPORT MEANS A LOT!</strong></span></h1>\r\n&nbsp;', 'THANK YOU, SUPPORTERS!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'thank-you-supporters', '', '', '2015-01-28 21:29:17', '2015-01-28 21:29:17', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=1219', 0, 'post', '', 0),
