(1428, 2, '2015-09-08 22:00:38', '2015-09-08 22:00:38', '<h1>Law Clinic - Please contact the toll free Access Pro Bono phone number to book an appointment.  <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">1-877-762-6664.</span></h1>\r\n<strong>Provided by <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Volunteer Lawyers</span></strong>.\r\n<h2><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">IMPORTANT NOTICE:</span></strong></h2>\r\n<h2><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">The Free Legal Clinic has moved to a new location.</span> </strong> <strong>The new address is #102 - 3301 24th Ave., Vernon BC.</strong></h2>\r\nDo you need some legal advice, or think you might? We can help you receive basic advice on legal issues from a lawyer.\r\n\r\n<em>Appointments are booked on a first come, first served basis.</em>\r\n\r\nSome issues may not be addressed at every clinic - you may have to wait for another session when a volunteer lawyer is available who can assist you.\r\n<h2>Attend the FREE Legal Clinic</h2>\r\nClinics are held on Thursdays of each month<em> (when a volunteer lawyer is available),</em> except statutory holidays.', 'Law Clinic', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '71-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-08 22:00:38', '2015-09-08 22:00:38', '', 71, 'http://localhost/wordpress/2015/09/71-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
