(1416, 2, '2015-08-10 20:16:42', '2015-08-10 20:16:42', '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Playhouse.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1265\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Playhouse-300x259.jpg\" alt=\"Playhouse\" width=\"195\" height=\"169\" /></a></p>\r\nVernon Women\'s Transition House Society would like to thank everyone who participated in our spring fundraiser <span style=\"color: #8f1717;\"><strong>\'Playhouses for Hope\'.</strong></span>  This amazing event raised over $5,000 to go towards our programs.  We are fortunate to be part of such a supportive community, and our thanks goes out to each and every person who bid on the playhouses in the silent auction and to the lucky winners.\r\n\r\nThis fundraiser would not have been possible without the tremendous work of the <em><strong>Village Green Centre/Bentall Kennedy staff</strong></em> <em><strong>as well as all the playhouse sponsors,</strong></em> who all spent many hours painting and decorating the playhouses.\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #8f1717;\">Our heartfelt gratitude goes out to</span></strong></h1>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>The Village Green Centre</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Bentall Kennedy</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Save-on-Foods</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Community Futures</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Hytec - A Kohler Company</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>The Bay</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Sun FM</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Coldstream Fire Department</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Cloverdale Paint</strong></p>', 'PLAYHOUSES FOR HOPE - THANK YOU', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'playhouses-for-hope-thank-you', '', ''